criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  healthy women, ASA class 1 (normal healthy) or class 2 (with mild systemic disease);

          -  undergoing IVF or ICSI and reaching the stage of egg collection;

          -  with ultrasonically diagnosed hydrosalpinx and identifiable during the phase of
             ovarian stimulation;

          -  giving written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  patients not giving written informed consent;

          -  patients cancelled for poor ovarian response;

          -  ultrasonically diagnosed hydrosalpinx and identifiable for the first time at
             egg-collection
